stockpiled while the united states has about 30000 tons however 
both those figures are thought to be largely underestimated 
the soviet foreign minister said his country while possessing 
chemical weapons has never used them has no chemical weapons 
stockpiles outside soviet territory and has never transferred 
chemical weapons to other nations 
he called on all countries to end production of chemical weapons 
the united states halted production of chemical weapons in 1969 
but resumed 18 years later to counter the soviet stockpiling 
